Third-party notices

This mod is an architectural port of the same author's Cemetery Overflow
Manager. The underlying capacity-scaling techniques — scaling prefab data
anchored to the authoring baseline, and restoring a value only if no other
mod has changed it since — derive from the MIT-licensed mod
"Magic Hearse + Funeral Director":

    Copyright (c) 2026 River-Mochi
    https://github.com/River-Mochi/MagicHearse
